{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_39","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed, but the wagon-specific generation itself appears to have succeeded. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2354-library-new-request-org.apache.maven.wagon-wagon-ssh-external-1.0-beta-2-f0ef0ff1. `logs/org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-12T22-56-15-039226Z.log` and `stats/org.apache.maven.wagon/wagon-ssh-external/1.0-beta-2/execution-metrics.json` show a successful generation run for `org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2` (5 iterations, 440 generated LOC). `stats/org.apache.maven.wagon/wagon-ssh-external/1.0-beta-2/stats.json` reports `0/0` dynamic-access calls, so dynamic-access coverage was not the failing signal here.\n\nThe most likely failing stage was local CI follow-up, not test generation. `logs/org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T22-57-12-729513Z.log` and `logs/org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2/local-ci-fixup/run-consecutive-tests-2026-05-12T23-01-17-864430Z.log` show the wagon native-image tests passing (`9 tests successful`, `PASSED:1.0-beta-2`). `logs/org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2/local-ci-fixup/changed-tested-versions-matrix-2026-05-12T22-59-25-536629Z.log` shows local CI had to restore the legacy `generateChangedTestedVersionsMatrix` task, and both `logs/changed-metadata-matrix/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-12T22-59-04-083214Z.log` and `logs/changed-metadata-matrix/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-12T23-01-05-831308Z.log` show the changed-metadata matrix unexpectedly included `com.typesafe.akka:akka-serialization-jackson_3:2.6.21` alongside wagon. The `run-consecutive-tests` fixup log then records that removing that accidental Akka scaffold made the wagon-only run pass.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Recreate or cherry-pick the wagon changes onto a clean branch that contains only `org.apache.maven.wagon:wagon-ssh-external:1.0-beta-2`.\n2. Decide whether this workflow still needs `generateChangedTestedVersionsMatrix`; if it does, keep the compatibility fix, otherwise update the workflow to use the consolidated changed-metadata task consistently.\n3. Rerun the changed-metadata matrix and `run-consecutive-tests` gates on the cleaned branch."}}
